            p.align-center Fashion goes mobile. Designing the official app for NYFW highlighting live/exclusive content and commerce opportunities from the shows, designers and experts.
            p.align-center Accessible fashion was the core focus of the HEED app.  Bringing the runway, experts and commerce opportunities to mobile through live, continuous content and unique interaction design.

      .wrapper
        .spacer.spacer-medium
        .wolf-item.wfull
